center kemerovo wanted to continue shipping coal that had been mined 
the coal miners are showing restraint and discretion and not 
yielding to inflammatory demands that the enterprises of other 
sectors be asked to join the strike the paper declared but press 
reports sunday said workers at 17 nonmining enterprises in the town 
of kiselevsk had struck in solidarity 
