threaten its security and stability 
unmediated peace talks began aug 25 five days after the 
truce and have gone nowhere 
in a separate development hashemi rafsanjani speaker of irans 
parliament and favorite in its july 28 presidential election said 
relations with the west could improve if approached on the basis of 
equality the official islamic republic news agency reported 
a foreign ministry statement for the anniversary of irans 
